<item>
            <title>[LU-4280] Test failure on test suite sanity-quota, subtest test_7d</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4280</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/459a88d4-520e-11e3-88be-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/459a88d4-520e-11e3-88be-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;maloo reports a high failure rate on this subtest&lt;br/&gt;
Failure Rate: 31.00% of last 100 executions &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;all branches&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;maybe needs some attention before it blocks too much testing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_7d failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-quota 7d&lt;/p&gt;</description>
